---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main class="layout">
      <aside class="sidebar">
        <h2 class="name">Anastasia Psarou</h2>
        <p class="email">
          <a href="mailto:anastasia.psarou@uj.edu.pl">anastasia.psarou@uj.edu.pl</a>
        </p>
        <img
          src="/images/anastasia.jpeg"
          alt="Photo of Anastasia Psarou"
          width="200"
          height="200"
          class="avatar"
        />
        <p class="tags">Multi-agent systems · Reinforcement learning · Agent-based modeling · Transportation</p>
      </aside>

      <section class="content">
        <p>
          <strong>Current role:</strong> I am a second-year PhD student at the
          <a href="https://www.uj.edu.pl/">Jagiellonian University</a>, working under the supervision of
          Professor <a href="https://www.rafalkucharskilab.pl/">Rafał Kucharski</a>.
          My research is conducted within the
          <a href="https://github.com/COeXISTENCE-PROJECT">COeXISTENCE</a> project, funded by the European Research Council (ERC).
        </p>

        <p>
          <strong>Research:</strong> My work investigates how autonomous vehicles make routing decisions.
          I develop multi-agent reinforcement learning models to simulate and optimize their interactions within dynamic traffic networks.
        </p>
		<p>
          <strong>News:</strong> 
		  <ul>
			<li>
				I am currently undertaking a six-month research visit at 
				<strong>ETH Zurich</strong> within the 
				<strong>Institute for Transport Planning and Systems (IVT)</strong>. 
				My work focuses on congestion pricing and fairness in multi-agent traffic systems, 
				leveraging multi-agent reinforcement learning methods. The visit is jointly supervised by 
				<a href="https://www.ivt.ethz.ch/en/people/profile.anastasios-kouvelas.html"> Dr. Anastasios Kouvelas </a> and <a href="https://www.michailmakridis.com/>"Dr. Michalis Makridis </a>, 
				and supported by the “Excellence Initiative – Research University” grant of Jagiellonian University.
			</li>

		  	<li>Our paper 
				<a href="https://example.com">
					<em>URB -- Urban Routing Benchmark for RL-equipped Connected Autonomous Vehicles</em>
				</a> 
				got accepted to NeurIPS 2025 in San Diego.
			</li>
			<li>
				Our paper 
				<a href="https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S2352711025002468">
					<em>RouteRL: Multi-agent reinforcement learning framework for urban route choice with autonomous vehicles</em>
				</a> 
				got published in SoftwareX journal.
			</li>

		  </ul>
		</p>
      </section>
    </main>
    <Footer />

    <style>
      /* Layout */
      .layout {
        max-width: 1100px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 2rem 1rem;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 280px 1fr;
        gap: 2rem;
        align-items: start;
      }

      /* Left column */
      .sidebar {
        position: sticky;
        top: 1rem; /* keeps the left panel visible while scrolling on desktop */
      }

      .name {
        margin: 0 0 0.25rem 0;
        font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 2.2vw, 1.8rem);
        line-height: 1.2;
      }

      .email {
        margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
        word-break: break-word;
      }

      .avatar {
        display: block;
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 220px;
        height: auto;
        border-radius: 8px;
        margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
      }

      .tags {
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        color: var(--text-dim, #555);
      }

      /* Right column */
      .content p {
        margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
        line-height: 1.65;
        font-size: 1.02rem;
      }

      /* Responsive */
      @media (max-width: 800px) {
        .layout {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
        .sidebar {
          position: static;
        }
        .avatar {
          max-width: 180px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </body>
</html>
